title: Who knows which Typeface this is?
content:
I’m looking for the typeface of the image you can see below.  
Is it a Slab Serif or a Display Font? I was looking for it but so  
far no matches from me.

| Attachment | Size |
| --- | --- |

author: Simexe

comments.content: It’s so thin I’ll bet it is custom, but here are some other [Extra Light Slabs](http://web.archive.org/web/20090726055322/http:/www.fontshop.com/fontlist/genres/extra_light_slab_serifs/?&sample_text=EXILES&sample_size=96).

You probably right. This type comes pretty close  
but the its always one letter which is different.  
But thanks a lot this will help me so far.
